videos.headline: Nix finds Stove for a wide-open Auburn TD
videos.description: Bo Nix hits Eli Stove for an easy 11-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Nix finds Stove for a wide-open Auburn TD) 2020/10/17 ESHEET

videos.headline: Harris pounds it in for the TD
videos.description: South Carolina's Kevin Harris pushes his way into the end zone to cut into Auburn's lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Harris pounds it in for the TD) 2020/10/17 ESHEET

videos.headline: Horn dives to pick off Nix's pass
videos.description: South Carolina DB Jaycee Horn picks off Bo Nix's pass in traffic to earn his first career interception.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Horn dives to pick off Nix's pass) 2020/10/17 ESHEET

videos.headline: Williams' jaw-dropping catch sets up a Bigsby TD
videos.description: Bo Nix airs out a 44-yard pass to Seth Williams to set up Tank Bigsby's first career touchdown for Auburn.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Williams' jaw-dropping catch sets up a Bigsby TD) 2020/10/17 ESHEET

videos.headline: Williams and Nix share frustrations on Auburn sideline
videos.description: Seth Williams and Bo Nix look heated on Auburn's sideline after a failed offensive play.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Williams and Nix share frustrations on Auburn sideline) 2020/10/17 ESHEET

videos.headline: Shi Smith Mosses defender for go-ahead TD
videos.description: 5-foot-10 Shi Smith leaps above an Auburn player to bring in the go-ahead Gamecock touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Shi Smith Mosses defender for go-ahead TD) 2020/10/17 ESHEET

videos.headline: Horn's interception leads to a Harris TD
videos.description: South Carolina's Jaycee Horn picks off Bo Nix for a second time to set up a touchdown for Kevin Harris.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Horn's interception leads to a Harris TD) 2020/10/17 ESHEET

videos.headline: Smith makes sensational catch while falling to the ground
videos.description: Shi Smith makes a ridiculous grab to advance South Carolina up the field.

videos.headline: Smith shows off impressive hands as South Carolina knocks off Auburn
videos.description: Gamecocks WR Shi Smith hauled in a pair of impressive catches as he helped South Carolina beat No. 15 Auburn.
